author: Gordon Lubold
title: American Killed in Raid to Rescue Kurdish Fighters in Iraq
text:
WASHINGTONâ€”American special operations forces conducted a raid with Kurdish peshmerga fighters inside Iraq and freed as many as 70 prisoners held by Islamic State in a rare, joint mission in which at least one American service member was killed, officials said.
A unit of as many as 30 U.S. special operations forces conducted the joint raid to free peshmerga fighters at a prison facility held by Islamic State in the town of Hawija,...
